          "briefTitle": "The Efficacy and Safety of Iparomlimab/Tuvonralimab (Anti PD-1/CTLA-4) Combined With Albumin-bound Paclitaxel in Second-line Treatment of Patients With Advanced Gastric/Gastroesophageal Junction Adenocarcinoma",
          "officialTitle": "The Efficacy and Safety of Iparomlimab/Tuvonralimab (Anti PD-1/CTLA-4) Combined With Albumin-bound Paclitaxel in Second-line Treatment of Patients With Advanced Gastric/Gastroesophageal Junction Adenocarcinoma"
        },
