          "detailedDescription": "This is a double-blind, randomised, placebo-controlled study evaluating the safety, tolerability, pharmacokinetics and pharmacodynamics of a single administration of ZE74-0282 at 5 dose levels in healthy volunteers. Evaluation of dose levels will be conducted in a sequential fashion with lower dose levels evaluated first in the sequence. Dosing in each cohort will start with two sentinel participants with one of the two sentinels randomised to receive ZE74-0282 and the other randomised to receive placebo. The safety and tolerability of each sentinel participant will be monitored in the clinic until Day 3 and will be reviewed prior to dosing the remainder of participants in each cohort."
